title: Arizona lawmakers vote to let public school districts spend money promised by state, prevents school closures
description: School districts in Arizona will be able to spend all the money they were promised by the state. This eliminates the risk of school closures and teacher layoffs.
author: Associated Press

title: State of the Union live updates: Biden address focuses on economy, health care
description: Follow along for live updates, latest coverage and expert analysis of President Joe Biden’s second State of the Union address.
author: Msnbc

title: Florida Legislature expands Ron DeSantis' program to fly migrants to blue states
description: Florida lawmakers passed a bill Friday expanding a program used to fly migrants to Democratic-led cities and states.
author: Adam Edelman and Amanda Terkel and Zoë Richards

title: 'I felt very unsafe': Gay fathers confronted at Arizona religious school accepting vouchers
description: Legal experts said there are limited judicial avenues for families that experience gender-related discrimination at religious schools.
author: Renata Cló, USA TODAY NETWORK
